YE DESCRIPTION
-
STUPID MVC is a stupid simple model-view-controller framework library thing written for PHP, versions 5.3 and up. It uses the PDO extension for database access so you should probably have that installed too.

It's really a very small, simple, little framework.


YE INSTRUCTIONS
-
Download from here, unzip into some path that's part of your include path, make the magic.

What? Need more documentation? Yeah. It's all on the Wiki, including configuration, app layout, etc, etc: http://wiki.github.com/wellsoliver/stupidMVC


